result.name: BRICK LANE (Admiralty)

reviews.text: The food looked good, but everything tasted pretty average to be honest. The interior appeared quite elegant with a rustic charm in its decor. However, the staff could definitely be a little friendlier and more sensitive to the customer's needs. A disengaged server totally dampens the atmosphere in the restaurant.

Very satisfying brunch! I had their pancake with seasonal berries and full English breakfast. Portion size of the full English breakfast was large and good for two to share. Service was great! Staff were attentive.

The setting is cozy. Service is great. My boy is fish allergy, they provide options for the salad dressing. The ribeye is good w a reasonable price. The truffle mushroom soup is creamy as it is filled with scent of truffle everywhere. 1 star off on the roasted spring chicken, too dry on the chicken breast.
Will def going back for other pasta.
The seasoning of food is awful😩 This restaurant is located at the grade A commercial building; you can enjoy a quiet place to dine at night there.
Lunch was decent and nice, but pricing is towards the higher end. Good for gathering.

However, the staff could definitely be a little friendlier and more sensitive to the customer's needs. A disengaged server totally dampens the atmosphere in the restaurant.

好耐都冇去BRICK LANE 食野，星期日咁啱同朋友去完野餐HEA完，之後就去中信大廈搵食。因為唔算好餓嘅關係，我地點左脆香雞翼同埋北海道帶子沙律。首先講下個雞翼先，本身我係一個雞翼腔，所以對雞翼都有要求。呢碟雞翼炸得好脆口，而且上到碟就已經聞到好香，我同朋友都一隻接一隻咁食。(之後叫多左一碟) 食咁多雞翼當然heavy啦，為左令自己個心舒服啲就食少少沙律啦。我好鍾意呢碟沙律有一種清新嘅感覺，同埋帶子唔算細粒，都幾juicy，一個人都可以KO得晒。最後我地點左兩杯白酒，結束呢個咁美好嘅週末。

Very satisfying brunch! I had their pancake with seasonal berries and full English breakfast. Portion size of the full English breakfast was large and good for two to share. Service was great! Staff were attentive.

話說今日有個FRD黎搵我食飯, 就去左BRICK LANE 食餐好既先~ 我地兩個人就叫左個晚餐，BRICK LANE 既環境好合適收左工去食餐好既到CHILL一 下，好relax. 同朋友去飲番杯，又或者情侶撐枱腳都係好好既選擇. 發達芝士牛油果雞沙律，好新鮮，而且色彩豐富。非常抵讚的前菜。是日餐湯為薯仔湯，薯仔湯好足料。個湯仲有個包仔食 個包一定要食 幾好味架! 新奧爾良燒海鮮
燒海鮮包括魚味香濃，入口爽滑鮮嫩，燒過後仍然好juicy的鱈魚!!!! 飲筒走塑既環保鐵飲筒配合到而家環保意識!
每次來也吃All day breakfast，夠飽，價錢也較合理

result.name: 有馬日本料理

reviews.text: Very bad service.  (1) Waitress always dark face.  Heart not into the job, not delivering what customers asked.      (2) Sashimi set a disgrace, only 4 pieces of sashimi plus some smaller thin slices into a flower pattern; and 75% were salmon (one of the cheapest fish), a zero price-quality.      (3) Bad management.  A table of dad mom and a about 3y.o. son, they were talking so loud that the entire restaurant can be heard (the restaurant was very quiet at the time, so it was not the environment neccesitating her to raise her voice), and the waitresses all joined in and played with her and her son also very loudly.    (4) ill qualified manager, I told him about the bad service and the sashimi set, he was clueless as if everything is supposedly that way, he could not even comprehend the customer’s concern.
Fine Japanese dining. Lunch is around $200+. It's a quiet place for working lunch, better than downstair's  steak house.
I ordered a set lunch but food was delivered in a wrong sequence.
Good Japan restaurant
